text: Lagache is a surname. Notable people with the surname include: *Alfred Lagache (1889 –1971), French professional three-cushion billiards player *André Lagache (1885–1938), French racing driver *Daniel Lagache (1903–1972), French physician, psychoanalyst and professor at the Sorbonne == See also == *Chardon Lagache (Paris Métro), station on the Paris Métro *Monchy-Lagache, commune in the Somme department in Hauts-de-France in northern France
